{"id": "1293462118380601405", "channel_id": "1293462118380601405", "type": 0, "author_id": "1274188474957828132", "author_name": "yingmai_", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2024-10-09T06:36:40.386000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 20}], "attachments": [{"id": "1293462118611550218", "filename": "24135ae727c42db5835a50a472c1b0fe.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 27617, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1293462118380601405/1293462118611550218/24135ae727c42db5835a50a472c1b0fe.jpg?ex=69fb8a38&is=69fa38b8&hm=90af7f162d6a9fa518ef2c92e5a269ba4b3d8a40f25c0b262ce40d276fb99fc2&"}, {"id": "1293462119026528358", "filename": "cbf1b86dfe0c9205e8f763e39a889a85.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 26589, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1293462118380601405/1293462119026528358/cbf1b86dfe0c9205e8f763e39a889a85.jpg?ex=69fb8a38&is=69fa38b8&hm=bc03adcaff86fd450acb2a5291caf43e5367deca2c19785655138212317bc093&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293462118380601405", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "【梗图】堆点我P过的梗图", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1293517915575816273", "channel_id": "1293517915575816273", "type": 0, "author_id": "1170753879617572915", "author_name": "niubi.plusv587", "author_bot": false, "content": "第一节  界域伊始\n\n祂从天中来，祂从地中来，祂从海中来，祂从书中来。\n\n赐下四礼，名之界域，予之天赋，化之四方。\n\n其一为生，生生而不息，气动而不止，是为混沌。\n\n其一为灭，狂战亦伤己，性烈而戮王，是为血肉。\n\n其一为变，借物以强身，三变以御敌，是为深海。\n\n其一为受，五逝而轮转，求一世之机，是为超维。", "timestamp": "2024-10-09T10:18:23.474000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 9}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293517915575816273", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却·提灯圣经·第六卷·界域书（自编）", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1293603285919465472", "channel_id": "1293603285919465472", "type": 0, "author_id": "1170753879617572915", "author_name": "niubi.plusv587", "author_bot": false, "content": "第一节  生而不存\n\n自远古来，其界荒渺，旧神已去，却无新主。\n\n融蚀漫漫，没入虚空，万畜不宁，无光无暗。\n\n难存之黯，难鸣之哀，难衷之诉，难承之苦。\n\n当是时，四海无波如死域，天矮地裂如灭境，生而难存，孚如死矣。", "timestamp": "2024-10-09T15:57:37.350000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293603285919465472", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却·提灯圣经·第三卷·苦难纪", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1182359790249332756", "1283686991728218245"]}
{"id": "1293604723248857249", "channel_id": "1293604723248857249", "type": 0, "author_id": "1170753879617572915", "author_name": "niubi.plusv587", "author_bot": false, "content": "第一节 暗若微芒\n\n幻灭三千，一朝闻声，祂自水中来，如琼浆，如玉液。\n\n天星暗淡，地脉翻滚，人间无亮，何日安宁。\n\n有二侍，一拥白石，谓之粟；一执长龙，谓之鱼。\n\n祂于其中，自诩为光，暗若微芒。", "timestamp": "2024-10-09T16:03:20.036000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1293604723248857249", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却·提灯圣经·第五卷·争斗书", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1182359790249332756", "1283686991728218245"]}
